{"_path":"/tags/frontend/css","_dir":"frontend","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"CSS","description":"CSS（Cascading Style Sheets）是用于描述文档样式和布局的样式表语言，用于控制网页的外观和样式。CSS定义了各种属性和值，用于设置元素的样式，如颜色、字体、间距、边框等","name":"css","icon":"logos:css-3","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"css"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CSS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"icon","props":{"className":["size-32"],"name":"logos:css-3"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CSS（Cascading Style Sheets）是用于描述文档样式和布局的样式表语言，用于控制网页的外观和样式。CSS 定义了各种属性和值，用于设置元素的样式，如颜色、字体、间距、边框等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CSS3 是 CSS 的第三个主要版本，引入了许多新的特性和功能，使得开发者能够实现更丰富、更复杂的样式效果。以下是 CSS3 相对于 CSS 的一些主要改进和新增功能："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"圆角边框"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CSS3 引入了"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"border-radius"}]},{"type":"text","value":"属性，可以实现圆角边框效果，而在 CSS 中需要使用背景图片来实现。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阴影效果"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CSS3 引入了"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"box-shadow"}]},{"type":"text","value":"属性，可以实现元素的阴影效果，而在 CSS 中通常需要使用背景图片来模拟。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"渐变背景"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CSS3 引入了"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"linear-gradient"}]},{"type":"text","value":"和"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"radial-gradient"}]},{"type":"text","value":"属性，可以实现元素的渐变背景效果，而在 CSS 中通常需要使用背景图片。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多列布局"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CSS3 引入了多列布局属性，可以实现元素的多列文本布局，而在 CSS 中通常需要使用浮动或表格布局。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"动画效果"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CSS3 引入了"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@keyframes"}]},{"type":"text","value":"规则和"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"animation"}]},{"type":"text","value":"属性，可以实现元素的动画效果，而在 CSS 中通常需要使用 JavaScript。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"媒体查询"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CSS3 引入了媒体查询（Media Queries），可以根据设备的特性和屏幕尺寸应用不同的样式，实现响应式设计。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总的来说，CSS3 相对于 CSS 具有更多的新特性和功能，使得开发者能够实现更加丰富、现代化的样式效果，提升了网页设计的灵活性和创造力。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":5,"depth":5,"links":[{"id":"css","depth":2,"text":"CSS"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:tags:frontend:css.md","_source":"content","_file":"tags/frontend/css.md","_extension":"md"}